│ where some unused lanes are non-poison, causing the assert to fire. A conservative, safe fix is to sanitize such mask lanes to PoisonMaskElem immediately before the assertion,          │
│ preventing the debug assertion and keeping the costing logic robust. I'll patch llvm/lib/Transforms/Vectorize/SLPVectorizer.cpp to insert this sanitization right above the assert, then │
│ run submit-patch.                                                                                                                                                                        │
│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
